# Source: docs/specs/03-spec-eval-cache-ci/03-spec-eval-cache-ci.md
# Pattern: CLI/Process
# Recommended test type: Integration

Feature: HTML Report Generation (SM6)

  Scenario: dotnet aieval CLI tool is installed as a local tool
    Given the project has a .config/dotnet-tools.json manifest
    When the developer runs "dotnet tool restore"
    Then the Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Evaluation.Console tool is available
    And "dotnet aieval --help" prints usage information with exit code 0

  Scenario: HTML eval report is generated from cached eval data
    Given the eval test suite has been run and cache data exists
    And the dotnet aieval tool is installed
    When the developer runs "dotnet aieval report"
    Then the command exits with code 0
    And an HTML report file is generated

  Scenario: Generated HTML report contains all eval scenario results
    Given an HTML eval report has been generated by "dotnet aieval report"
    When the report is opened
    Then the report contains results for all eval scenarios
    And each scenario shows its evaluation outcome
